{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"75d9b8fbe3","title":"在一次干部会上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c7aee5cd03","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"干部和干部政策","id":"3df4ae75e1","type":"主题"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"指导理论","id":"c1c0033e04","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"林彪","id":"cce608ea44","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3ec9d22784","type":"title","text":"在一次干部会上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45b042d2f1","type":"paragraph","text":"农村上下左右一起搞，两个席卷，一个震动。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"07305dee33","type":"paragraph","text":"一、农村","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7a142a3e7","type":"paragraph","text":"① 积极搞文化大革命。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c50bffc5e8","type":"paragraph","text":"② 农村实行大民主。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"01752f6b5a","type":"paragraph","text":"③ 不愿意搞的不勉强。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f5acb6b190","type":"paragraph","text":"④ 革走资本主义道路当权派和地富反坏右的命。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e37243cba0","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤ 依靠贫下中农和红卫兵。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"568e7fd4a6","type":"paragraph","text":"⑥ 达到抓革命促生产的目的。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e39c917ada","type":"paragraph","text":"二、我们要有足够的精神准备，要受得了。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e55183e7f","type":"paragraph","text":"① 对干部的认识问题，我们过去把现状维持派当成好干部，好听现状维持派的话，没有弄清那些是革命的，那些是不革命的。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1e9fcc9af","type":"paragraph","text":"② 现在又发生了“痞子”问题。最闹革命的终归有缺点，现在看，要允许人家革命。怎样看待这些人是当前最大的问题。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"923d0c9d5a","type":"paragraph","text":"③ 如何认识这次运动。这次运动是大批判、大审查、大教育运动，也就是一个批判干部的运动。既批判走资本主义道路的当权派，也批判走社会主义道路的当权派，不过性质不同，开始也很难分清楚。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d65efbc3d","type":"paragraph","text":"④ 如何安排自己。革命革到自己头上来了，如何对待，现在干部距离很大。有四种情绪：第一种抱怨情绪；第二种抱对立情绪；第三种抱抵触情绪；第四种抱无可奈何情绪。只有一条，紧跟主席思想，否则就抛开。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0c9001929","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤ 斗争很尖锐，很复杂。首先搞通自己思想，要检查一下。为什么过去我们落后思想容易接受？为什么精神不振？为什么运动以来“怕”字当头？不解决这些问题不行，一定要垮台。现在左派反对我们好得很，因为我们犯了路线错误。右派反对我们也好，还有黑帮反对我们，这就看你们顶得住顶不住。有人说自己没有执行资产阶级反动路线，这很值得深思。总之两句话，大民主，人人可以出来讲话，看你怎么办？","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7171b75b7","type":"paragraph","text":"⑥ 号召同志们学习十五期《红旗》社论。新的形势，两个利用，两个反对，五个标准。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1633aeb9dc","type":"paragraph","text":"⑦ 现在干部有五种情况：","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9dc8426f9","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）能跟上主席思想，在游泳中已经游过去了。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80a82878f6","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）在游泳中淹得够呛，但也算游过去了。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52c2711067","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）  跟得很吃力，结果还是淹死了。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8edb1df851","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）不下水不革命。口头上也说几句革命的话，但什么都是人家的不对。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"782b9fff85","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）也在那里游，但确实身体不好，游到半途了。这些水平不高，认识跟不上去，往前没有力气了，对这种人大家要帮助一下。这次运动是全面的考查干部，看你是怎样对待革命的，怎样对待群众的，怎样对待自己的。","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"08898cef4f","type":"paragraph","text":"刊载于《高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗》（林彪文集），1967年4月编印，编印者不明。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d9b8fbe3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}